quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not lifted up your heart
  94,2,and removed your burden
  94,3,"that weighed so heavily on your back, and"
  94,4,have We not given you high renown
  94,5,"So, surely with every hardship there is ease"
  94,6,"surely, with every hardship there is ease"
  94,7,"So, when you are free, strive hard"
  94,8,"and to your Lord turn [all] your attention"